node.text:
Hello! 

Here is a quick montage of the Maì Striped sweater being knitted. This is not a tutorial, but if you have any questions, feel free to reach out! 📧 

You can find the full pattern in the shop. Would love to see your progress, as you work on your piece, as well as your finished result. 🧶 ✨ #maìknit

A day working on my pots. ✨
Music by @iksonofficial - Blossom

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Maì. on September 08, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
Landscape sweaters are back tomorrow! ☀️💕

Our hand knitted Merino wool sweaters return this Thursday at 3pm BST in both the Spring and Autumn colour-ways. Joining them are also more Fungo teapots and Tsuika planters! ✨

Please note your sweater will take 1-5 weeks to ship as they are hand crafted by our lovely knitters 🧶

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Maì. on September 06, 2021. May be an image of toy.

node.text:
The sun is setting at Bear Park so you only have a little time left to enter our raffle 🌤🌳

Purchase our new Bear Park digital illustration and you will be entered into a prize draw to win one of these one of a kind ceramic creations handmade by Marzia! Plus 100% of our profits will be donated to @hsiglobal 💕

Raffle ends Tuesday September 7th at 3pm BST. Follow the link in our bio if you’d like to enter ✨🌿

node.text:
If you go down to the woods today you're sure of a little surprise! 🧸🌳🧺

Time for another charity raffle! We’re heading to Bear Park, where everyone greets you with a smile! 🙂

Purchase our new Bear Park digital illustration and you will be entered into a prize draw to win one of these one of a kind ceramic creations handmade by Marzia! Plus 100% of our profits will be donated to @hsiglobal💚

Raffle ends Tuesday September 7th at 3pm BST. Good luck!

Hello! 

Here is a quick montage of the Maì Striped sweater being knitted. This is not a tutorial, but if you have any questions, feel free to reach out! 📧 

You can find the full pattern in the shop. Would love to see your progress, as you work on your piece, as well as your finished result. 🧶 ✨ #maìknit

node.text:
Light or dark? Which would you choose? 🤍💍🖤

We’ve added two new colour-ways to our sparkly Iro collection! One ring is surrounded by delicate clear stones while the others are a moody jet black 🥀 

Jewellery preorder is open now and runs until September 8th at 3pm BST. Shipping in October ✈️

node.text:
That’s Maì kind of daisy chain! 🌼✨

The Maì Daisy collection is now available in our store, consisting of a sparkly new necklace, bracelet and pair of stud earrings. We also have new additions to the Iro set in the form of white and black colour-ways along with the return of all Notte pieces and some new moon and star stud earrings. 🌙⭐️

Pre-order available until September 8th at 3pm BST. Shipping in October 📦

Head to shopsanrio.com to explore our new collab now 💕

node.text: Maì Accents are pleased to offer these charming detached properties to the market. Full of character and benefiting from a spacious open plan interior with hand painted detailing and an original wood structure. An ideal starter home for your tissue box. Visit our site to secure yours today🔑🏠💕

node.text:
Introducing The Roseum Ring, our latest collaboration with @lumen.thelabel! Carefully crafted in Vicenza, Italy by a single artisan and customisable from the material to the engraving ✨🌿

Head to @lumen.thelabel for all the details. Pre-order is open until August 31st at 4pm BST🌙🤍

node.text:
Jump into in-the-round knitting with our new stripy knitting pattern! 💕🧶

This sweater is beginner friendly, and knits up quickly in super chunky yarn. Head to the Maì store for all the details and to start your next knitting project. Have fun!🎉

Our Fungo teapots and Tsuika planters are back in stock tomorrow August 11th at 3pm BST! Joining them are more Casetta tissue box holders AND a new knitting pattern! 🌸🌤
